es<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/photos-et-videos-biblotheque\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20221026_095848_1-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3479\" width=\"95\" height=\"126\" srcset=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20221026_095848_1-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20221026_095848_1-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20221026_095848_1-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20221026_095848_1-1536x2048.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20221026_095848_1-scaled.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 95px) 100vw, 95px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/photos-et-videos-biblotheque\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082104-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3470\" width=\"94\" height=\"124\" srcset=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082104-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082104-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082104.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 94px) 100vw, 94px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/photos-et-videos-biblotheque\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/288606048_400011358594685_5008811664955696999_n-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3455\" width=\"98\" height=\"130\" srcset=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/288606048_400011358594685_5008811664955696999_n-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/288606048_400011358594685_5008811664955696999_n-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/288606048_400011358594685_5008811664955696999_n.jpg 780w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 98px) 100vw, 98px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/photos-et-videos-biblotheque\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082036-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3468\" width=\"101\" height=\"134\" srcset=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082036-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082036-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG_20190703_082036.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 101px) 100vw, 101px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Pour plus de photos et vid\u00e9os <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/photos-et-videos-biblotheque\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"3498\">CLIQUEZ ICI!<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la Biblioth\u00e8que<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u2019acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la biblioth\u00e8que est r\u00e9serv\u00e9 uniquement aux :<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Enseignants de la facult\u00e9.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Etudiants en poste graduation.<\/li><li>Chercheurs externes munis d\u2019une demande d\u2019autorisation d\u2019acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la biblioth\u00e8que.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"has-blue-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:20px\">Inscription \u00e0 la biblioth\u00e8que<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u2019entr\u00e9e \u00e0 la biblioth\u00e8que est libre et gratuite. Une inscription annuelle vous permet d\u2019acc\u00e9der \u00e0 la biblioth\u00e8que, d\u2019emprunter des documents et de b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier des autres services offerts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pour confirmer votre inscription vous devez pr\u00e9senter :<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Une carte de Biblioth\u00e8que pour l\u2019ann\u00e9e en cours ou une carte de biblioth\u00e8que. <\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Une copie d\u2019une pi\u00e8ce d\u2019identit\u00e9 et une copie d&#8217;un certificat de scolarit\u00e9 de l\u2019ann\u00e9e en cours, <\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Pour les usagers externes hors l\u2019universit\u00e9 de Bab Ezzouar, doivent pr\u00e9senter le dossier suivant :<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Une autorisation d\u2019acc\u00e8s sign\u00e9 par l\u2019\u00e9tablissement d\u2019origine, <\/li><li>Une attestation de travail de l\u2019ann\u00e9e en cours pour les enseignants, <\/li><li>Une copie de la carte National, <\/li><li>Une Photo.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-blue-color has-text-color\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\">Horaires d&#8217;ouverture<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>Dimanche&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u00e0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mercredi<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>De&nbsp;&nbsp; 8h00&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u00e0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 17h00<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>Jeudi&nbsp; de 8h00&nbsp;&nbsp; \u00e0&nbsp; 16h00<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center has-white-color has-blue-background-color has-text-color has-background wp-block-heading\">Organigramme de la biblioth\u00e8que d&#8217;Informatique<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/organigramme-faculte-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3482\" width=\"856\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/organigramme-faculte-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/organigramme-faculte-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/organigramme-faculte-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/organigramme-faculte.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 856px) 100vw, 856px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Catalogue de la facult\u00e9<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Une base de donn\u00e9es en ligne du fonds documentaire de la biblioth\u00e8que est accessible \u00e0 travers le&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/catalogue-de-la-faculte-dinformatique\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"3485\">Catalogue de la facult\u00e9<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/bib-info\/opac\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/bib-info\/opac\">Syngeb\/OPAC<\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\">Recherche<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Il existe deux types de recherche :<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Manuelle<\/strong> (acc\u00e8s libre).<\/li><li><strong>Informatis\u00e9e<\/strong> : une base de donn\u00e9es du fonds documentaire de la biblioth\u00e8que(SYNGEB) permet une recherche multi crit\u00e8res et par type de document.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fonds et Statistiques<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Le fonds documentaire de la Biblioth\u00e8que d\u2019Informatique est constitu\u00e9 de :<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Monographies : environ <strong>9168 <\/strong>titres \/ <strong>8953<\/strong> titre en fran\u00e7ais\/<strong>194<\/strong> titre en anglais \/<strong>021<\/strong> titre en arabe&nbsp;<\/li><li>Revues : <strong>80<\/strong> titres<\/li><li>Collections rassembl\u00e9es : <strong>04<\/strong> collections&nbsp;<\/li><li>Th\u00e8ses : Doctorat<strong> 150<\/strong>\/Master <strong>2741<\/strong>\/&nbsp; Licence <strong>4257<\/strong> \/ing\u00e9niorat <strong>391<\/strong><\/li><li>Articles scientifiques : 387 articles<\/li><li>Pr\u00e9publications&nbsp;: <strong>117<\/strong><\/li><li>Cd &amp; dvd<strong> 6805<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"has-blue-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\"><strong>Statistiques Mensuelles du Pr\u00eat et d&#8217;Adh\u00e9rents \u00e0 la Biblioth\u00e8que<\/strong><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Chaque fin du mois, il est mis \u00e0 la disposition des adh\u00e9rents des statistiques relatives:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Aux livres emprunt\u00e9s.<\/li><li>Au nombre d&#8217;adh\u00e9rents emprunteurs.<\/li><li>A l\u2019ouvrage le plus emprunt\u00e9 au cours du mois en question.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"has-blue-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\"><strong>Nouvelle acquisition de livres<\/strong><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Chaque ann\u00e9e la biblioth\u00e8que ach\u00e8te de nouveaux ouvrages selon les besoins des adh\u00e9rents&nbsp;&nbsp; enseignants, \u00e9tudiants&nbsp; (en moyenne 40 \u00e0 65 titres constitu\u00e9s de 2 \u00e0 4 exemplaires chacun).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Les nouvelles acquisitions des ouvrages, sont affiches&nbsp; (la diffusion de l\u2019information) par rapport aux nouveaux ouvrages acquis.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/documents-administratifs-bibliotheque\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/graduation-g5df5471ed_1280-1024x755.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3493\" width=\"156\" height=\"114\" srcset=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/graduation-g5df5471ed_1280-1024x755.png 1024w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/graduation-g5df5471ed_1280-300x221.png 300w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/graduation-g5df5471ed_1280-768x566.png 768w, https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/graduation-g5df5471ed_1280.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 156px) 100vw, 156px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Documents Administratifs<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/contacts-bibliotheque\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/contacts-bibliotheque\/\">@Contact<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color wp-block-heading\" style=\"color:#f20c0c\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/actualites_bib_informatique\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"3645\">\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0646\u0627\u062a \u0645\u0643\u062a\u0628\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0622\u0644\u064a<\/a><\/h1>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Facult\u00e9&nbsp; d\u2019Informatique \u0645\u0643\u062a\u0628\u0629 \u0643\u0644\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0644\u064a BIBLIOTHEQUE D\u2019INFORMATIQUE Version en arabe MOT DE RESPONSABLE DE LA BIBLIOTHEQUE Nous sommes heureux <span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/presentation-bibliotheque\/\">Suite<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3647,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-447","page","type-page","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/447"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=447"}],"version-history":[{"count":35,"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/447\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4171,"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/447\/revisions\/4171"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3647"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=447"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}